comments: Minkovsky reads off of pre-prepared slides everyday for weeks until the test. Her lectures are boring and monotonous, so unless you are really interested in the material, it\'s hard to pay attention. She is a fair grader, though, and has clear expectations. But when tests come, and you haven\'t been paying attention, it can be hectic.
